name: Matt's Local Pharmacy
vaccines: Janssen COVID-19 Vaccine, Moderna COVID-19 Vaccine
info: ●●● ENGLISH: This clinic is offering the Moderna and Johnson & Johnson (Janssen) COVID-19 vaccines which are for people age 18 or older only. The Moderna vaccine requires two doses. The Johnson & Johnson vaccine requires one dose. ●●● ESPAÑOL: Este centro ofrece las vacunas contra el COVID-19 de Moderna y Johnson & Johnson (Janssen) que son solo para personas mayores de 18 años. La vacuna de Moderna requiere de dos dosis. La vacuna de Johnson & Johnson requiere de una sola dosis. ●●● PORTUGUÊS: Essa clínica está oferecendo as vacinas da Moderna e da Johnson & Johnson (Janssen) contra a COVID-19, que são para pessoas com 18 anos de idade ou mais. A vacina da Moderna requer duas doses. A vacina da Johnson & Johnson requer uma dose.
special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
